<p><strong>One of Unit 6's two design partners.</strong> The Equity &amp; Resilience Partner argues the case the Urban Planner will not: protect green and blue space, keep land permeable for flood resilience, design for heat comfort, and above all do not solve a neighbourhood's problems by displacing the people already living there. It is the urban version of pushing for ecology and justice together. It helps you reason about who a plan serves and who it costs, and it keeps informal settlements and affordability in view when optimisation alone would quietly erase them.</p>

